```plantuml
@startuml UoA-eResearch_hub-stack

actor User
participant "ResearchHub Website (Frontend)" as Frontend
participant "GraphQL API (cer-graphql)" as GraphQL
participant "Contentful CMS" as Contentful
participant "Search Proxy (hub-search-proxy)" as SearchProxy
participant "ElasticSearch" as ElasticSearch
participant "AWS Cognito" as Cognito
participant "Jenkins CI/CD" as Jenkins
participant "Terraform" as Terraform
participant "AWS Cloud" as AWS

User -> Frontend: Access website
Frontend -> Cognito: Authenticate user
Cognito --> Frontend: Authentication token

Frontend -> GraphQL: Query content (with token)
GraphQL -> Contentful: Fetch content
Contentful --> GraphQL: Return content
GraphQL --> Frontend: Return formatted content

Frontend -> SearchProxy: Search request (with token)
SearchProxy -> ElasticSearch: Execute search
ElasticSearch --> SearchProxy: Return results
SearchProxy --> Frontend: Return formatted results

group Deployment Process
  Jenkins -> Terraform: Trigger infrastructure deployment
  Terraform -> AWS: Provision resources (S3, CloudFront, Lambda, etc.)
  AWS --> Terraform: Confirmation
  Terraform --> Jenkins: Deployment status

  Jenkins -> Frontend: Build and deploy frontend
  Frontend -> AWS: Upload to S3/CloudFront
  AWS --> Frontend: Confirmation
  Frontend --> Jenkins: Deployment status

  Jenkins -> GraphQL: Build and deploy API
  GraphQL -> AWS: Deploy to ECS/ECR
  AWS --> GraphQL: Confirmation
  GraphQL --> Jenkins: Deployment status

  Jenkins -> SearchProxy: Build and deploy Lambda
  SearchProxy -> AWS: Deploy Lambda function
  AWS --> SearchProxy: Confirmation
  SearchProxy --> Jenkins: Deployment status
end

@enduml
```